00:10:37.880 --> 00:10:39.480
Saya tidak percaya ini!

00:10:40.480 --> 00:10:41.960
Artinya Aparajita

00:10:42.640 --> 00:10:44.600
ingin bunuh diri!

00:10:44.760 --> 00:10:46.520
Oh wow!

